The Facebook post, a paid advertisement from PSD Iași, wishes women a happy Women's Day.  While the advertiser is a political party, the content itself is not electoral propaganda. The timing of the post (March 8th, International Women's Day) further supports the conclusion that the post's primary purpose is not related to the parliamentary elections.
